1
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:26,220
(Notice)
Welcome to an Immersive Life Simulation.

2
00:00:26,980 --> 00:00:33,140
Welcome to Door of Truth,
an open-world social deduction game.

3
00:00:33,140 --> 00:00:36,020
You will enter the dungeon world
as a player

4
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:38,740
and begin your adventure.

5
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:41,480
This game includes four cases.

6
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,720
(Case 1, Case 2, Case 3, Case 4)
In each case,

7
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:45,800
(Characters)
you will unlock a new character

8
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:47,920
and experience a different life path.

9
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:49,680
By exploring

10
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:51,760
and interacting with NPCs,

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:54,880
you will uncover each story,

12
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,000
solve the case,

13
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,480
and find the culprit.

14
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:59,200
(Case 1, 2, 3, 4 completed)
Complete all cases

15
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:01,160
to earn the completion achievement

16
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,800
(Completion Achievement)
and unlock the hidden ending.

17
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,480
Each case

18
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:05,600
(Case 1, Case 2)
may contain one

19
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,160
or more investigations.

20
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,400
(Random, Detective, Suspect)
When the case begins,

21
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,400
you will be randomly assigned

22
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,360
as a detective or suspect.

23
00:01:11,880 --> 00:01:14,160
(Suspect, NPC)
The true culprit may be

24
00:01:14,160 --> 00:01:15,520
a suspect player or an NPC.

25
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,400
(Culprit)
Choose carefully.

26
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:19,240
The culprit's goal

27
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,720
is to remain hidden.

28
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:23,400
(Culprit)
Only the true culprit may lie.

29
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,760
(Main Quest, Evidence, Exploration, Rewards)
During the investigation,

30
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:27,200
(Skill Card, Trial, Stamina points, Side Quest)
different game mechanics

31
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,800
can be triggered to advance the case.

32
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,800
Use them wisely

33
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,400
for an unexpected breakthrough.

34
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,800
(Suspect, Culprit, NPC)
After the investigation,

35
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,520
the culprit vote begins.

36
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,680
If the culprit is identified,

37
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,120
(Correct Vote, Culprit)
players who voted correctly

38
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:42,200
receive a Golden Key.

39
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,840
If the player is the culprit

40
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,680
(Culprit, Players)
and receive fewer votes,

41
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:48,200
(Culprit, Vote, Players)
that culprit earns a Golden Key.

42
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,960
(Players)
Golden Keys are awarded

43
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:52,560
after the case ends.

44
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,920
(Skill Card)
They can be exchanged for Skill Cards.

45
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,860
(Notice All persons, backgrounds,)
Please confirm.

46
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:58,840
(and descriptions are fictional.)
Notice

47
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,650
(Settings and actions are setups.)
Dungeon world loading complete.

48
00:02:00,650 --> 00:02:02,690
(All photos and videos)
Please immerse yourselves

49
00:02:02,690 --> 00:02:04,010
(are authorized.)
in the experience.

50
00:02:04,010 --> 00:02:04,340
(Safety measures were taken
during shooting. Don't try this at home.)

51
00:02:04,340 --> 00:02:04,780
(Parental supervision required
for underage viewers.)

52
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:05,860
(Loading)

53
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:10,700
(Loading...)

54
00:02:10,700 --> 00:02:13,220
(Dungeon Pass)

55
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:19,380
(The Truth)

56
00:02:20,420 --> 00:02:24,460
=The Truth=

57
00:02:24,500 --> 00:02:29,700
(Tui City, June 1, Year 260 of Tui)

58
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,120
Everyone, five days ago,

59
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:39,080
we solved a major case.

60
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:42,800
So the new ruler of Tui City,
Chancellor Tui

61
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,600
invited us...

62
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:44,960
To a banquet.

63
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:45,920
... to a banquet at Zuixian Inn today.

64
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,560
(Five Days Ago)
Chancellor Tui will arrive soon

65
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:50,720
and take over the affairs of Tui City.

66
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,320
Chancellor Tui.

67
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:52,920
(11:00AM)

68
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:53,160
Right.

69
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,040
(Zuixian Inn)
He wants to meet us at noon.

70
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,880
I didn't expect such an important figure

71
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:59,000
to invite us to a banquet.

72
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:02,280
Everyone looks dressed up.

73
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:02,920
Exactly.

74
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,480
Who do you think you are?

75
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,360
Who are you

76
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,520
to talk like that?

77
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,680
Come on, drag him out.

78
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,640
Wounded Ke.

79
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,500
(Today's Wounded Look)

80
00:03:11,940 --> 00:03:12,460
(Wuxia Style, Passionate Young Hero)

81
00:03:12,460 --> 00:03:13,060
(Asymmetrical high-slit outer robe)

82
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:13,660
(Stylish yet easy to move in)

83
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:14,260
(Armor details, heroic warrior style)

84
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:14,900
(Wuxia Style, Cool Female Hero)

85
00:03:14,900 --> 00:03:15,660
(High-waisted layered scholar skirt)

86
00:03:15,660 --> 00:03:16,380
(Elegant yet smart and capable)

87
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:17,060
(Delicate silver accessories
add refined details)

88
00:03:17,060 --> 00:03:17,700
(Wuxia Style, Martial Arts Master)

89
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:18,420
(Wide sleeves and flowing cloak
with wraparound straps)

90
00:03:18,420 --> 00:03:19,100
(Vintage and majestic)

91
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:19,820
(Half-tied hair with a simple crown,
mature and refined)

92
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:20,820
(Exotic Style, Calm Noble)

93
00:03:20,820 --> 00:03:21,700
(Silver jewelry and leather armor,
sleek and mysterious)

94
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:22,700
(Wide leather belt
accentuating the waist)

95
00:03:22,700 --> 00:03:23,500
(Enhancing body proportions)

96
00:03:23,940 --> 00:03:24,500
(Exotic Style, Princess)

97
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:25,260
(Red-gold embroidery and beading)

98
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:26,100
(Full vintage gold
and silver accessories)

99
00:03:26,100 --> 00:03:26,660
(Vibrant vintage elegance, noble status)

100
00:03:26,860 --> 00:03:27,540
(Exotic Style, Noble Prince)

101
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:28,300
(Fine pearls
and silver-thread embroidery)

102
00:03:28,300 --> 00:03:29,100
(Gentle divine aura)

103
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:29,740
(Light silver-gold tied hairstyle)

104
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:32,020
Hey, hey, hey.

105
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:34,840
Chancellor Tui has arrived!

106
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,920
He looks like Tang Bohu.

107
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,480
They look

108
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:42,960
like the Ghostly Duo.

109
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,480
The Ghostly Duo.

110
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,560
Wait, this looks like a street thug.

111
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,760
Look at that little bounce.

112
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:00,880
Move.

113
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:04,820
(Chancellor Tui, played by Xu Guodong)

114
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,520
You're all very punctual.

115
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,600
Please, come inside.

116
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,400
Well, let's go.

117
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:08,720
Let's go.

118
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:09,800
Come on.

119
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,840
Here, take this.

120
00:04:14,340 --> 00:04:16,020
(Vibe ruined)

121
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:19,640
Why does your outfit

122
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,070
look so much like Chancellor Tui's?

123
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:21,720
Right.

124
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,360
Don't focus on me too much.

125
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,200
Could you be

126
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:26,540
his daughter?

127
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:27,760
(Wild imagination)

128
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,040
Don't question me.

129
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:30,400
Careful, I might fight back.

130
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:33,280
You seem excited today.

131
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:34,560
I've barely said anything.

132
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,680
It's summer now.

133
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,480
Come in.

134
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:40,480
Have a seat.

135
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:53,040
Everyone.

136
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,200
Do you know

137
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,960
why I invited you here today?

138
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,820
To treat us to a meal.

139
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:00,080
(Meal)
To reward us?

140
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:00,720
Wrong.

141
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,560
(Reward)

142
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,120
Wrong.

143
00:05:02,860 --> 00:05:04,000
(Yang Glory, played by Yang Chaoyue)

144
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:06,040
Did you invite us
to investigate something?

145
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:11,080
I invited you here for a tea gathering.

146
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:12,840
(Tea gathering)

147
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:13,800
Tea gathering.

148
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,960
Somehow I had a feeling

149
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,920
it was for a tea gathering.

150
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,280
I came

151
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:20,360
to honor you all

152
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:23,240
for solving the case a few days ago

153
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:23,720
and

154
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,160
to see

155
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,840
the true faces

156
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,600
of these heroes.

157
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:30,280
But there are two who aren't heroes.

158
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:34,320
Actually, those two
are the greatest heroes.

159
00:05:34,340 --> 00:05:36,040
(What a smooth talker)

160
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,800
That's right. We're

161
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,660
the defenders of the weak.

162
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,080
What?

163
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,160
The defenders.

164
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,440
Take down whoever is stronger.

165
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,120
(Big confidence)

166
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,600
Take down whoever is stronger?

167
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:45,960
Right.

168
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:48,080
Does that mean taking me down?

169
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:49,560
Of course not.

170
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:50,920
We fight evil and defend justice.

171
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,860
(A clever idea strikes)

172
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,520
(I'm the good one)
Fight evil and defend justice.

173
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,680
He's so easy to fool.

174
00:05:58,700 --> 00:06:00,660
(A little praise works)

175
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:01,680
Well.

176
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:01,920
Right.

177
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:02,720
I'll give it a try.

178
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:04,960
(The ultimate foodie)
I almost forgot

179
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:05,840
to let you take turns.

180
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:09,920
Who said you could eat?

181
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:11,800
Our girl is naive.

182
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,920
She's just a young girl.

183
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:15,440
You should learn some social etiquette.

184
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:18,240
She's totally spoiled. We all love her.

185
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,240
She's our baby.

186
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:20,760
Don't spoil her too much.

187
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:24,520
(He Ha, played by Zhang Linghe)
I invited

188
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:27,160
a royal chef for everyone.

189
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,800
Now you've got my attention.

190
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,000
Impressive.

191
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:36,960
(Chef Yang, a culinary legend,
played by Yang Kang)

192
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,160
Introduce

193
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,800
the pastries to everyone.

194
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,440
Serve the pastries.

195
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:42,160
There's more?

196
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,880
Serve the pastries.

197
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:43,280
Someone.

198
00:06:43,280 --> 00:06:44,400
Look,

199
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,640
there's more.

200
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:46,340
(Players' extra scenes)

201
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:47,100
(12PM every Sat)

202
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,160
Come on.

203
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:51,180
(Wow)

204
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:53,500
(Wow, wow, wow)

205
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,440
Look.

206
00:06:55,340 --> 00:06:56,500
(A little chaotic)

207
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:57,600
What's all this noise?

208
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:01,760
These must be
the most popular pastries now.

209
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:03,440
(Authentic pastries)

210
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,540
The one on the pineapple
is a pineapple tart.

211
00:07:05,540 --> 00:07:06,560
(Pineapple tart)

212
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:09,080
It symbolizes a thriving family

213
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,120
and lasting good fortune.

214
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,660
(Delicious)

215
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,480
Not bad.

216
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:17,240
So good.

217
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,600
After I eat this,

218
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,760
my whole family came alive.

219
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,920
(The rise of pineapple tart)
Your family came alive?

220
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:23,760
He means prosperous.

221
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,560
Prosperous indeed.

222
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,040
Aren't you an orphan?

223
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,340
A prosperous family.

224
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,360
(Forgot about that)
A prosperous family.

225
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,480
You must have hit the jackpot.

226
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,080
Remember what you said.

227
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:33,780
(Could He Ha have a secret?)

228
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,760
(Tieguanyin with a chocolate center)
This is made

229
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,680
with premium Tieguanyin from Anxi,

230
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:40,080
combined with western...

231
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,200
Chocolate.

232
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,020
(Chocolat)

233
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,680
Chocolat.

234
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,120
Chocolat!

235
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,520
Chocolat.

236
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,880
(Chopsticks can pick anything)
Its texture is rich and smooth,

237
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,720
enhancing its aroma.

238
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,160
It's so hard.

239
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,240
Pretty good.

240
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:58,240
(Ke Stubborn, played by Zhou Keyu)
Nice.

241
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,560
Come on, let's toast with the pineapple.

242
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,880
Come on, cheers!

243
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:02,240
A toast with pineapple.

244
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,240
I'm on top.

245
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,440
I'm the eldest here.

246
00:08:05,380 --> 00:08:06,380
(Stepped on)

247
00:08:07,340 --> 00:08:09,980
(Your little troublemaker)

248
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:10,880
Thank you, Chef Yang.

249
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:17,600
Now that we've had our fill,

250
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,080
let's discuss business.

251
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,160
Okay.

252
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,320
Did you really think

253
00:08:27,400 --> 00:08:28,720
you could hide your identities

254
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,680
from me?

255
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,040
What are you gonna do?

256
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,600
(Bold as always)

257
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,670
It was completely wiped out

258
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:36,720
five years ago.

259
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,200
(Fists clenched)

260
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,880
Tui Kingdom's rebels.

261
00:08:40,550 --> 00:08:41,600
Longdong Army.

262
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:48,280
But someone has survived

263
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,400
for the past five years.

264
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,400
Survived?

265
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:57,060
(One of the six is Longdong Army)

266
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:58,480
There's Longdong Army?

267
00:08:58,480 --> 00:08:59,680
Shouldn't you be dead?

268
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:02,120
There's Longdong Army.

269
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:04,000
Do you still want to live?

270
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,320
If there's only one...

271
00:09:22,380 --> 00:09:23,580
(Ah!)

272
00:09:23,780 --> 00:09:25,180
(Ahhh!)

273
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:26,660
(Night vision mode)

274
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,280
Hold on.

275
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,000
Okay, we're good.

276
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,880
Someone!

277
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:31,880
Someone help!

278
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,040
Chancellor Tui is dead!

279
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,480
Help!

280
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,960
The culprit must have
done something just now.

281
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,440
Definitely.

