(General Dong, who died five years ago?)

567
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:09,520
General Dong's son.

568
00:19:10,020 --> 00:19:11,980
(What a dramatic pause!)

569
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:12,960
Dong.

570
00:19:12,980 --> 00:19:15,140
(Ning Waver, Young General Dong)
Young General Dong.

571
00:19:15,820 --> 00:19:17,980
(Tui Kingdom: Ning Waver,
Young General Dong)

572
00:19:17,980 --> 00:19:20,140
(Ning Waver: Young Master of Chivalry Manor,
Young General Dong)

573
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,840
Young General Dong.

574
00:19:22,840 --> 00:19:24,800
You little "Dong" thing.

575
00:19:25,280 --> 00:19:26,680
Little Dong?

576
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:28,640
I am indeed Young General Dong.

577
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:29,400
Okay.

578
00:19:29,600 --> 00:19:31,440
General Dong and my master,

579
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:32,920
Shi Damen,

580
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:34,960
were

581
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:36,640
true kindred spirits.

582
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,640
But each followed his own calling.

583
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:40,160
What were their callings?

584
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,400
They were written on that painting.

585
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:44,360
(May Heaven protect all,)
Qide stayed in the martial world

586
00:19:44,360 --> 00:19:45,520
(as Longdong defends the realm.)

587
00:19:46,000 --> 00:19:47,160
to protect the common people.

588
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:48,520
As for Longdong,

589
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:51,160
(May Heaven protect all,)
his duty was to defend the realm

590
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,400
(as Longdong guards the realm.)
and guard the frontier.

591
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:56,320
He's indeed the son of a true hero.

592
00:19:56,320 --> 00:19:57,060
(Impressed)

593
00:19:57,360 --> 00:19:58,160
However,

594
00:19:58,680 --> 00:20:00,040
when I was very young,

595
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:02,240
my father, General Dong,

596
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:04,920
sent me to my master, Shi Damen,

597
00:20:05,020 --> 00:20:06,320
(Ning Waver's life timeline)

598
00:20:06,320 --> 00:20:07,960
(Born in Year 260 of Tui)
so he could raise me.

599
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:09,600
But when I

600
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:10,840
(Raised by Shi Damen)

601
00:20:10,840 --> 00:20:11,960
turned thirteen,

602
00:20:12,060 --> 00:20:13,520
(Age 13)

603
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:13,920
I...

604
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:15,440
made up my mind

605
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,040
to join the army.

606
00:20:17,100 --> 00:20:17,840
(Enlisted)

607
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:18,680
I became a soldier.

608
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:20,160
While I was there,

609
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,200
I met

610
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:23,800
a very close friend,

611
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:24,520
Dian.

612
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:26,400
He was

613
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:28,480
(Young General Dong is Dian's friend)
the adopted son of an army cook.

614
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:29,840
He was three years younger than me.

615
00:20:29,840 --> 00:20:30,600
Back then,

616
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,040
he was rather chubby.

617
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:33,780
A chubby little boy?

618
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:34,360
That's right.

619
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:36,360
Where's the pot?

620
00:20:36,360 --> 00:20:37,160
The pot.

621
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:39,000
That's right.

622
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:41,520
It says, "Young General Dong's
personal pot".

623
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:42,440
(The general's personal pot)
Because he was my best friend,

624
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:44,240
he'd always
cook something special for me

625
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:45,160
and make all my favorite dishes.

626
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,360
In return,

627
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:47,720
I taught him martial arts,

628
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:48,560
and we became

629
00:20:48,560 --> 00:20:50,160
the closest of friends.

630
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:52,840
But in Year 255 of Tui,

631
00:20:52,840 --> 00:20:56,360
war between Tui and Li
was about to break out.

632
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:56,840
That's right.

633
00:20:56,840 --> 00:20:57,720
I'm sure you all know about it.

634
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:00,360
You're all connected
to it too, aren't you?

635
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:04,060
(Everyone has something to hide)

636
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:07,080
Maybe just a tiny bit.

637
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:07,520
Alright.

638
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,080
That January,

639
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,520
before dawn on January 10,

640
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:13,120
an army

641
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:14,480
of 300,000 Li soldiers

642
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:16,600
launched a surprise attack
on the Longdong Army.

643
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:18,040
(Tui Kingdom)
My good friend

644
00:21:18,040 --> 00:21:19,520
rushed off to send a signal

645
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:20,960
and call for reinforcements.

646
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:22,400
Meanwhile,

647
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,760
I mounted my horse

648
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:25,360
and charged into battle.

649
00:21:25,360 --> 00:21:26,720
(Footage sourced online)

650
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:29,760
But the Li forces
greatly outnumbered us.

651
00:21:29,760 --> 00:21:30,680
They had 300,000 soldiers,

652
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,360
while the Longdong Army had only 10,000.

653
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:34,880
(Longdong Army vs. Li Army)
We fought and fought,

654
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:37,280
but no matter how many we struck down,

655
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:38,640
more just kept coming.

656
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:40,920
(Young General Dong)
Eventually, I was completely exhausted

657
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,920
and was rescued from the battlefield.

658
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,760
When I woke up again,

659
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,040
I found myself

660
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:47,360
at Chivalry Manor,

661
00:21:47,360 --> 00:21:48,320
the home of Shi Damen.

662
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,680
It turned out my master had saved me.

663
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,280
The first thing he told me

664
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:53,360
was that the Longdong Army

665
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:56,080
had been branded traitors
by the emperor.

666
00:21:56,100 --> 00:21:57,240
(The Longdong Army are traitors?)

667
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:58,480
They were framed.

668
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,640
Of course. They must've been framed.

669
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:00,240
They were framed.

670
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:00,600
Right.

671
00:22:00,940 --> 00:22:03,180
(Detectives' intimidating stare)
You seem awfully anxious.

672
00:22:03,580 --> 00:22:04,300
(An amused smile)

673
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,320
You'll be in for a real shock later.

674
00:22:05,340 --> 00:22:07,000
(Foreshadowing his character)

675
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:09,600
On January 8, Year 256 of Tui,

676
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:10,400
my master

677
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:12,440
decided to protect me

678
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,040
by giving me
a new identity and appearance.

679
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,680
So this face

680
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,960
isn't actually
Young General Dong's face.

681
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:20,040
I thought it was for the best.

682
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,800
This way, I could secretly investigate

683
00:22:21,800 --> 00:22:22,560
who

684
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,960
framed the Longdong Army.

685
00:22:24,960 --> 00:22:27,280
I must avenge my father

686
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:31,360
and my late friend, Dian.

687
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:32,640
Brilliant.

688
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:35,640
What a tragic and heroic story.

689
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:36,320
But...

690
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:37,800
(Innocent)
But I had nothing to do with his death.

691
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,080
That last part...

692
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:44,760
You really didn't need to add that.

693
00:22:45,440 --> 00:22:46,760
(That's enough, Ning)
You little Dong thing.

694
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:48,320
Go back, little "Dong" thing.

695
00:22:48,380 --> 00:22:50,460
(Humbled)

696
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:51,680
Let's see

697
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:55,160
what else they brought out earlier.

698
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,040
There's a secret code.

699
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:03,080
"Since Heaven
has given me another chance,"

700
00:23:03,080 --> 00:23:07,040
"I must send those
who deserve to die straight to hell."

701
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:14,400
Come to think of it...

702
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:17,320
Wait, when did he
come back from the dead?

703
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:18,880
Come back from the dead?

704
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:22,800
"Since Heaven
has given me another chance..."

705
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,760
It was when he was rescued.

706
00:23:29,380 --> 00:23:32,700
(January 8, Year 256 of Tui)

707
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:35,480
So, 0108... What was the rest?

708
00:23:39,380 --> 00:23:41,300
(Unlocked successfully)

709
00:23:42,160 --> 00:23:43,920
Yes.

710
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,800
That's it.

711
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:53,520
To the Marshal of Li...

712
00:23:53,520 --> 00:23:54,860
Regarding our previous agreement...

713
00:23:54,940 --> 00:23:56,120
All the terms...

714
00:23:56,120 --> 00:23:56,760
I'll read it.

715
00:23:56,760 --> 00:23:57,480
I have agreed...

716
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,880
How are you reading that?

717
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:00,880
You're pausing in all the wrong places.

718
00:24:01,340 --> 00:24:04,620
To the Marshal of Li...

719
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:05,400
Let me try.

720
00:24:05,960 --> 00:24:07,120
What kind of phrasing is that?

721
00:24:07,120 --> 00:24:08,120
That sounds awful.

722
00:24:09,260 --> 00:24:10,540
To the Marshal of Li.

723
00:24:10,540 --> 00:24:12,060
Regarding the terms previously discussed,

724
00:24:12,060 --> 00:24:13,340
I have agreed to them.

725
00:24:14,360 --> 00:24:15,440
How was that any different from mine?

726
00:24:16,560 --> 00:24:17,640
When the war begins,

727
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,600
(Meaning: I agree to what we discussed.)
I will surrender the city.

728
00:24:19,600 --> 00:24:20,200
As for the promised gold,

729
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,120
silver, land,

730
00:24:21,120 --> 00:24:22,320
and title...

731
00:24:22,320 --> 00:24:23,760
(When war begins,
I will surrender the city.)

732
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:25,920
I trust you'll keep your promise.

733
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:26,720
(As for the promised gold,)

734
00:24:26,720 --> 00:24:28,160
(I trust you'll keep your promise.)
My decision is final.

735
00:24:28,600 --> 00:24:30,160
There will be no turning back.

736
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:31,640
Once you receive this letter,

737
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:33,120
no need to reply me.

738
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:36,120
Respectfully, General Dong.

739
00:24:36,320 --> 00:24:37,160
General...

740
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:38,360
(Respectfully, General Dong.)
Wasn't he supposed to be a good man?

741
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:39,480
How could he do such a thing?

742
00:24:40,040 --> 00:24:41,920
He betrayed his kingdom
and doomed his people.

743
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,160
(General Dong committed treason)
General Dong was a traitor.

744
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:46,720
No.

745
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,160
This says...

746
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,960
At last, the forged seal...

747
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:51,600
At last, the forged seal
is indistinguishable from the real one.

748
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:53,480
We can secretly
report him to the emperor

749
00:24:53,480 --> 00:24:56,120
and have the Longdong Army wiped out.

750
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:57,680
They framed General Dong

751
00:24:58,040 --> 00:24:59,760
for conspiring with the Li Kingdom.

752
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:01,520
That made him look like a traitor.

753
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:03,080
And over here is

754
00:25:03,080 --> 00:25:05,080
a forged copy
of General Dong's military seal.

755
00:25:05,140 --> 00:25:08,340
(Who framed General Dong?)

756
00:25:08,880 --> 00:25:11,640
You were the one who found this?

757
00:25:12,600 --> 00:25:13,240
That's right.

758
00:25:13,920 --> 00:25:15,040
Five days ago,

759
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:17,760
I planned to take Lord Tui down with me.

760
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:19,440
But somehow...

761
00:25:19,440 --> 00:25:20,520
Even I don't know

762
00:25:20,520 --> 00:25:22,280
how I survived.

763
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:24,800
Not only did I survive,

764
00:25:25,160 --> 00:25:26,280
I also discovered

765
00:25:26,280 --> 00:25:28,320
the enemy I'd spent five years

766
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:29,640
searching for.

767
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:32,920
How did you find them?

768
00:25:32,920 --> 00:25:33,440
Who is it?

769
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:34,880
It's one of

770
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:37,720
the four of you.

771
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:39,720
I'm one of the good guys.

772
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:41,080
(Certified good guy)
It probably has nothing to do with me.

773
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,600
Quick to clear your name, aren't you?

774
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:44,240
(I'm not buying it)
Among the four of you,

775
00:25:44,240 --> 00:25:46,480
one is a despicable villain.

776
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,920
I found this letter in their room.

777
00:25:49,360 --> 00:25:49,840
So,

778
00:25:49,840 --> 00:25:51,760
I secretly
had their identity investigated.

779
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:52,880
And I discovered something.

780
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,240
That despicable villain

781
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,280
is one of the four of you.

782
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:56,120
One of you

783
00:25:56,120 --> 00:25:57,360
is from the Li Kingdom.

784
00:25:57,380 --> 00:26:03,700
(Someone here is from the Li Kingdom)

785
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:04,640
Who is it?

786
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:06,320
You'd better step forward now.

787
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,120
Someone from Li Kingdom?

788
00:26:09,120 --> 00:26:10,520
I've heard

789
00:26:10,520 --> 00:26:12,960
that the Li Kingdom

790
00:26:12,960 --> 00:26:14,840
send its children

791
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:15,680
to the Tui Kingdom

792
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:17,920
as spies from a very young age.

793
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,880
Okay.

794
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:22,040
A spy from Li.

795
00:26:22,040 --> 00:26:23,240
A Li secret agent.

796
00:26:26,560 --> 00:26:27,000
Okay.

797
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:28,360
Have you confirmed their identity?

798
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:29,480
Of course.

799
00:26:31,480 --> 00:26:33,280
That despicable villain...

800
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:37,160
is...

801
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:44,920
you!

802
00:26:46,000 --> 00:26:47,040
Yang Glory.

803
00:26:48,960 --> 00:26:49,160
Me?

804
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:51,320
Yang Glory.

805
00:26:51,320 --> 00:26:52,960
Your real name is...

806
00:26:53,940 --> 00:26:55,660
Li Shishui.

807
00:26:55,740 --> 00:26:57,420
(Yang Glory is Li Shishui?)
I'm not...

808
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:57,920
Impossible!

809
00:26:58,580 --> 00:26:59,580
Who are you?

810
00:26:59,580 --> 00:27:01,060
Li Shishui.

811
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:03,440
You sound like you're making this up.

812
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:04,640
Making it up?

813
00:27:06,360 --> 00:27:07,760
You're still denying it after all this?

814
00:27:08,120 --> 00:27:08,840
Still trying to argue?

815
00:27:08,840 --> 00:27:10,400
The Li Kingdom's birth records.

816
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,800
(Li Kingdom birth record)

817
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:13,440
The head of household is blurred.

818
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:14,440
The wife's name is blurred too.

819
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:17,360
The new family member is Li Shishui.

820
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:21,200
Sunflower-shaped birthmark
on the back of the neck.

821
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:26,640
I can't believe...

822
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:27,880
I'm actually Li Shishui.

823
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:34,440
- Li Shishui.
- Li Shishui.

824
00:27:34,540 --> 00:27:35,820
(Yang Glory is Li Shishui)

825
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:37,320
How did I know...

826
00:27:38,320 --> 00:27:38,920
it was her?

827
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,920
That day,

828
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:42,400
when she went to eavesdrop

829
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:43,800
on Lord Tui and me,

830
00:27:43,800 --> 00:27:44,800
do you remember how I rescued you?

831
00:27:45,120 --> 00:27:46,560
I tore off

832
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:47,560
the sunflower emblem on your clothes.

833
00:27:48,040 --> 00:27:49,400
Whose clothes are these?

834
00:27:49,400 --> 00:27:50,200
They're mine.

835
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:51,920
I wore them
when I followed the man in black.

836
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:52,760
Then,

837
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:53,760
I was nearly discovered.

838
00:27:53,760 --> 00:27:54,120
And then...

839
00:27:54,120 --> 00:27:54,960
Someone pulled you away.

840
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:56,880
He grabbed me
by the collar and rescued me.

841
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:57,840
At that moment,

842
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,600
I noticed another sunflower underneath.

843
00:28:00,540 --> 00:28:02,900
(Yang Glory, Li Shishui)
A sunflower within a sunflower.

844
00:28:03,640 --> 00:28:04,600
"Sunflower Glory".

845
00:28:06,860 --> 00:28:08,500
(Tui Kingdom:
Ning Waver, Young General Dong)

846
00:28:08,540 --> 00:28:10,900
(Li Kingdom: Yang Glory, Li Shishui)

847
00:28:10,900 --> 00:28:11,820
(Dian)

848
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:12,840
You'd better explain yourself.

849
00:28:12,840 --> 00:28:13,800
(Tell us the truth)

850
00:28:13,800 --> 00:28:15,320
I don't want to hear her explanation.

851
00:28:16,520 --> 00:28:17,640
Well, I do.

852
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,360
Go on. Explain.

853
00:28:18,360 --> 00:28:19,320
(Trying to sound intimidating)

854
00:28:19,320 --> 00:28:21,120
Why was this found in your room?

855
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:23,280
Sis, I really don't know!

856
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,920
If she doesn't know,
stop questioning her.

857
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:25,860
(Nobody picks on my sister)

858
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:27,720
You're a detective.

859
00:28:28,200 --> 00:28:29,720
Aren't you supposed
to be fair and impartial?

860
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:32,640
Are you the "wife"

861
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,760
listed here?

862
00:28:33,760 --> 00:28:34,520
(Head of household. Wife)

863
00:28:34,520 --> 00:28:35,920
Let me ask everyone this.

864
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,520
(Wrong, but still loud)
Didn't you already ask her?

865
00:28:37,520 --> 00:28:39,320
And didn't she say she didn't know?

866
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:40,480
So doesn't that settle it?

867
00:28:40,480 --> 00:28:41,760
I don't need her to know.

868
00:28:41,760 --> 00:28:43,240
It doesn't matter.
I don't want to hear it anyway.

869
00:28:43,240 --> 00:28:43,920
Like I said,

870
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:45,280
I don't want to hear her explanation.

871
00:28:45,440 --> 00:28:46,400
Fine. She's not going to do it.

872
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:47,280
Isn't that exactly what you wanted?

873
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:50,280
She doesn't even want to hear it,

874
00:28:50,280 --> 00:28:51,880
so why are the rest of you
getting worked up?

875
00:28:51,900 --> 00:28:53,460
(Exactly!)

876
00:28:53,540 --> 00:28:54,820
(Extremely dependent on her sister)

877
00:28:55,760 --> 00:28:57,000
(Alright)
If you...

878
00:28:57,840 --> 00:29:00,040
Stop letting your personal feelings
cloud your judgment.

879
00:29:00,100 --> 00:29:02,220
(Overprotective sister)

880
00:29:02,240 --> 00:29:05,240
I think we've established the grudge
between these two,

881
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:08,680
but the victim today was Chancellor Tui.

882
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,480
(Stay rational)
Right.

883
00:29:09,840 --> 00:29:11,010
(Case summary. Victim: Chancellor Tui)
We need to find his killer.

884
00:29:11,010 --> 00:29:11,640
(Place of death: Zuixian Inn)

885
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,320
(Cause of death: Poisoning?
Killer: Unknown)

886
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:13,760
I don't know.

887
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:14,520
I already told you,

888
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:15,560
I had nothing to do with his death.

889
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:16,300
(Ning Waver's motives:)

890
00:29:16,300 --> 00:29:16,940
(Against Yang Glory:
Suspects she is a spy from Li)

891
00:29:16,940 --> 00:29:17,540
(and wants to avenge his father's death
by killing her)

892
00:29:17,540 --> 00:29:18,100
(Against Chancellor Tui: None)

893
00:29:18,120 --> 00:29:20,400
All this proves is
that you're from Li, right?

894
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:21,000
Right.

895
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,720
The civilians are still innocent people.

896
00:29:23,040 --> 00:29:23,400
No.

897
00:29:26,160 --> 00:29:29,200
The people of Li
killed our people in Tui.

898
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,400
See? You're blinded by hatred.

899
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,480
I'll handle this later.

900
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:34,040
(I'm here)
I'll calm everyone down.

901
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:35,800
I'm the goddess of peace.

902
00:29:38,560 --> 00:29:41,680
Blinded by hatred?

903
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:44,880
Both armies lost 300,000 soldiers.

904
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:46,920
But the common people are innocent!

905
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,960
(Going on the attack)
Weren't the soldiers common people too?

906
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,200
(Immediately joins in)
Millions of them were displaced.

907
00:29:51,200 --> 00:29:52,560
I'm a commoner.

908
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:53,680
You're not a commoner.

909
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,480
You're...

910
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,400
You're a spy!

911
00:30:01,620 --> 00:30:03,380
(This is outrageous!)

912
00:30:03,460 --> 00:30:04,520
(This is outrageous!)

913
00:30:04,520 --> 00:30:06,000
Who's

914
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,080
the detective here?

915
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,640
So what? I'm a general!

916
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:09,720
And what are you? Sit down!

917
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,680
Let me tell you,

918
00:30:13,680 --> 00:30:14,520
you'll find out soon enough.

919
00:30:14,520 --> 00:30:16,600
You have the lowest status here.

920
00:30:16,600 --> 00:30:17,800
You're just an innkeeper.

921
00:30:18,120 --> 00:30:19,640
(She's met her match)
You're just an innkeeper.

922
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:21,760
Okay.

923
00:30:21,760 --> 00:30:22,800
Today,

924
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:25,200
I'm casting one vote. I...

925
00:30:26,040 --> 00:30:27,200
Let's see how you talk
your way out of this.

926
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,360
Soon,

927
00:30:28,360 --> 00:30:30,320
everyone will see her true colors.

928
00:30:30,320 --> 00:30:31,520
That little snake.

929
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:32,600
Wait.

930
00:30:32,600 --> 00:30:34,440
(Little snake)
Go ahead! Search me!

931
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,880
To the woodshed!

932
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:42,640
Search the cook!

933
00:30:45,060 --> 00:30:45,660
(Rest and recharge)

934
00:30:45,660 --> 00:30:46,260
(Rest resets battle fatigue.
Recharging restores energy)

935
00:30:46,260 --> 00:30:46,820
(If you want to survive this quest,)

936
00:30:46,820 --> 00:30:47,340
(treat rest and recharging
like passive skills)

937
00:31:17,360 --> 00:31:19,320
(Zuixian Inn)
Have some fruit.

938
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:20,000
Peaches?

939
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:21,440
Plums.

940
00:31:22,480 --> 00:31:23,440
You're from Li Kingdom.

941
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:24,800
So you love plums, right?

942
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:25,380
(Evidence +1)

943
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:27,800
People from Li Kingdom love plums.

944
00:31:27,800 --> 00:31:29,080
What about people from Tui Kingdom?

945
00:31:30,840 --> 00:31:31,240
Tui...

946
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:31,920
They like...

947
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:32,440
Pushing hair.

948
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:32,920
Push...

949
00:31:32,920 --> 00:31:33,640
Pushing heads.

950
00:31:34,800 --> 00:31:36,640
You sure you wanna go first?

951
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:39,000
This is my turf.

952
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,000
What's there to be scared of?

953
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:40,880
Then you go first.

954
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:41,260
(Off you go)

955
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:41,680
Woodshed.

956
00:31:42,620 --> 00:31:43,660
(New location unlocked: Woodshed)

957
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:44,680
Well, there's the wood.

958
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,680
Alright, guys.

959
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:48,720
I'm innocent.

960
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:49,440
(I've been framed!)

961
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:50,120
Innocent?

962
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:52,000
My lords, I'm innocent!

963
00:31:54,460 --> 00:31:56,740
(I'll eat first)

964
00:31:56,780 --> 00:31:57,900
(Unlock the detective team's
best moments early)

965
00:31:57,900 --> 00:31:59,060
(At every Tuesday noon,
Dungeon Unlocking)

966
00:31:59,060 --> 00:32:02,340
(Daily top-up)

967
00:32:04,040 --> 00:32:05,160
What's this?

968
00:32:06,120 --> 00:32:06,760
What's that?

969
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:09,680
This.

970
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:11,000
(Those blueberries paid off)
This mark. Look.

971
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:12,760
There's a kite underneath.

972
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:13,700
(A letter)

973
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:15,460
(Thousand-Faced Eagle King mark)
It's the Thousand-Faced Eagle King.

974
00:32:16,160 --> 00:32:18,160
A thousand faces hide among us.

975
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:20,940
(Why is the mark in the woodshed?)
One righteous cause saves all.

976
00:32:23,040 --> 00:32:25,160
Actually, I

977
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:26,480
founded the Thousand-Faced Eagle King.

978
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:29,260
(Yang Glory, founder of the
Thousand-Faced Eagle King)

979
00:32:29,280 --> 00:32:31,080
The Thousand-Faced Eagle King
is a group?

980
00:32:31,080 --> 00:32:31,600
Right.

981
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:33,000
We don't have a leader.

982
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:34,800
It's made up of countless
ordinary people

983
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:36,120
who came together on their own.

984
00:32:36,140 --> 00:32:38,700
(Thousand-Faced Eagle King
is a civilian organization)

985
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:41,320
We do heroic deeds
to protect the people.

986
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:44,480
We gather intel
on threats to the people.

987
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,800
These kites are used

988
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:47,080
to send messages.

989
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:47,360
Right.

990
00:32:47,360 --> 00:32:48,080
(Messages are sent by kite)
They carry messages.

991
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:48,960
Is there a letter on it?

992
00:32:49,360 --> 00:32:49,800
Yes.

993
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:52,740
(Why is the letter blank?)

994
00:32:54,040 --> 00:32:54,600
Wait.

995
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:57,080
No, there are marks on it.

996
00:32:57,520 --> 00:32:58,520
(How do we reveal the writing?)
You need to...

997
00:32:58,520 --> 00:32:59,280
Rub it with a pencil.

998
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:00,320
Do we have charcoal dust?

999
00:33:00,320 --> 00:33:00,760
Charcoal dust.

1000
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:04,620
(Oil, water, vinegar)

1001
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:10,480
Vinegar, water, oil?

1002
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,340
(Vinegar)

1003
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,480
You can spray it.

1004
00:33:12,480 --> 00:33:13,640
(Theory: These reveal the writing)
Spray it.

1005
00:33:16,080 --> 00:33:16,680
Yes.

1006
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:24,800
Who?

1007
00:33:24,800 --> 00:33:25,800
The name at the top was crossed out.

1008
00:33:25,860 --> 00:33:27,180
(The name was secretly crossed out)

1009
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:29,520
It's someone powerful in Tui Kingdom.

1010
00:33:29,520 --> 00:33:30,760
They forged

1011
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:31,840
a secret letter

1012
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:33,640
from the Longdong Army

1013
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,760
and presented it to the emperor,

1014
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:37,600
framing the Longdong Army

1015
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:39,480
for treason and colluding
with the enemy.

1016
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:42,360
They tried to pit Tui and Li

1017
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:43,560
against each other again.

1018
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:47,360
Their evil ambition is plain to see.

1019
00:33:47,360 --> 00:33:48,480
They can't be forgiven.

1020
00:33:48,500 --> 00:33:51,180
(Who is this powerful figure
from Tui Kingdom?)

1021
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,480
So what you found

1022
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:54,040
was evidence she'd collected.

1023
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:55,860
(The secret letter Ning Waver found)
She didn't make it.

1024
00:33:55,880 --> 00:33:56,920
That's evidence I collected.

1025
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:59,600
I found this letter in her room.

1026
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:02,240
I finally forged the seal perfectly.

1027
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:04,080
Now I can report it to the emperor

1028
00:34:04,080 --> 00:34:05,600
and frame General Dong.

1029
00:34:06,020 --> 00:34:07,340
(The evidence Ning found
was collected by Yang)

1030
00:34:07,380 --> 00:34:08,900
(Front-row seat to the drama)

1031
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:10,520
See? You jumped to conclusions.

1032
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:12,000
Wait.

1033
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:13,150
I don't believe it!

1034
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:14,520
Let's see what else is here.

1035
00:34:14,540 --> 00:34:16,300
(I have to find proof of treason)

1036
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:22,280
This...

1037
00:34:25,400 --> 00:34:26,280
Dong.

1038
00:34:26,280 --> 00:34:27,140
(Dong)

1039
00:34:27,220 --> 00:34:28,040
(The same iron pot)

1040
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:28,920
Wait.

1041
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,400
Your best bro can cook?

1042
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:31,960
She's the cook.

1043
00:34:31,980 --> 00:34:34,260
(How is Yang Glory connected to Dian?)

1044
00:34:34,560 --> 00:34:36,190
Is your best bro a man or a woman?

1045
00:34:36,220 --> 00:34:37,760
(Even he can't answer that right away)

1046
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:38,120
I...

1047
00:34:38,670 --> 00:34:40,600
I'm actually that little brother
of yours.

1048
00:34:40,600 --> 00:34:42,820
(Yang Glory is Dian)

1049
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:47,840
The story of Mulan...

1050
00:34:48,190 --> 00:34:49,280
It really is...

1051
00:34:50,080 --> 00:34:50,670
Then, didn't I

1052
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:52,080
go warn you? When I came back,

1053
00:34:52,080 --> 00:34:52,840
you were gone.

1054
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:58,080
Then why didn't you recognize her?

1055
00:34:58,080 --> 00:34:59,560
Did she change her appearance too?

1056
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:01,120
Her hair wasn't long back then.

1057
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:01,360
Right.

1058
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:02,600
Then when I came back,

1059
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:03,600
everyone had been wiped out.

1060
00:35:03,600 --> 00:35:04,760
So I joined

1061
00:35:04,760 --> 00:35:06,640
the Thousand-Faced
Eagle King to investigate

1062
00:35:06,640 --> 00:35:07,320
and gather intel.

1063
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:09,680
I wanted to find
whoever did this to you.

1064
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:11,860
(Yang Glory is actually Dian)

1065
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:12,880
Oh no.

1066
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:15,760
I mistook my little brother
for my enemy!

1067
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:18,360
Ning!

1068
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:20,040
You just did that in front of everyone!

1069
00:35:20,040 --> 00:35:22,360
Just like that!

1070
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:25,560
But your birth certificate

1071
00:35:25,560 --> 00:35:27,880
proves you're from Li Kingdom.

1072
00:35:28,520 --> 00:35:29,560
I am from Li Kingdom,

1073
00:35:29,560 --> 00:35:31,240
but I was abandoned.

1074
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:32,200
So in Tui City,

1075
00:35:32,200 --> 00:35:34,000
I was adopted by my foster parents.

1076
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,720
Then I followed him into the army.

1077
00:35:35,920 --> 00:35:37,320
Does where she's from even matter?

1078
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,520
She's Dian.

1079
00:35:39,520 --> 00:35:41,280
She's Dian!

1080
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:43,080
She cooked for you every day

1081
00:35:43,080 --> 00:35:44,560
and went to light the beacon for you!

1082
00:35:44,560 --> 00:35:45,360
She said, "Ning,"

1083
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,640
"wait for me to come back"!

1084
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:48,120
Ning,

1085
00:35:48,120 --> 00:35:49,120
it's me!

1086
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:53,840
Hurry up and reunite!

1087
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,600
Come on!

1088
00:35:56,040 --> 00:35:57,320
Aren't we getting a big reunion scene?

1089
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:57,800
It's me!

1090
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,160
"The broken pot is whole again".

1091
00:35:59,440 --> 00:36:00,480
Dian!

1092
00:36:00,480 --> 00:36:01,920
Brother and sister reunited!

1093
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:04,680
Let me get my pot!

1094
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:05,080
Wait.

1095
00:36:05,080 --> 00:36:05,840
Okay.

1096
00:36:06,900 --> 00:36:11,060
(Hurrying)

1097
00:36:11,080 --> 00:36:11,680
Ning.

1098
00:36:18,620 --> 00:36:22,020
(Live accompaniment)

1099
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:24,000
It really is you, Dian!

1100
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:24,560
Yes.

1101
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,120
Back then,

1102
00:36:27,120 --> 00:36:29,720
my original name was Xiao Diandian.

1103
00:36:29,720 --> 00:36:30,920
My dad thought

1104
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,560
dressing me as a boy

1105
00:36:32,560 --> 00:36:32,880
would make it easier...

1106
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,600
To protect yourself.

1107
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:34,480
Right. It was easier.

1108
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:36,120
Later, to investigate all this,

1109
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:37,320
I changed my name

1110
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,160
to Yang Glory

1111
00:36:38,160 --> 00:36:39,160
and came to her inn.

1112
00:36:39,640 --> 00:36:40,720
Say no more.

1113
00:36:40,720 --> 00:36:41,480
Yang,

1114
00:36:42,160 --> 00:36:44,920
when your brother
was yelling in your face,

1115
00:36:45,080 --> 00:36:48,480
you must've been heartbroken!

1116
00:36:49,640 --> 00:36:50,080
Yeah!

1117
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:52,320
I even called you a little snake.

1118
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,620
Now you're his

1119
00:36:55,620 --> 00:36:57,440
(Baby little snake)
precious little snake.

1120
00:36:58,320 --> 00:36:59,760
I misunderstood you.

1121
