1146
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:41,320
I don't care if I leave fingerprints!

1147
00:37:41,320 --> 00:37:42,200
I'm killing him!

1148
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:43,160
Can we get a fight scene?

1149
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:43,600
Here's the thing.

1150
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:45,180
Here's the thing.

1151
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,640
I'm not a big shot from Tui Kingdom.

1152
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:48,600
I am...

1153
