Where's "literally"?

1156
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:54,960
Your name is Big Shot?

1157
00:37:54,960 --> 00:37:55,640
Exactly.

1158
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:56,760
His name is Big Shot.

1159
00:37:56,760 --> 00:37:58,000
I'm just a Big Shot.

1160
00:37:58,000 --> 00:37:59,760
Not a big shot from some kingdom.

1161
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:00,360
Exactly.

1162
00:38:00,380 --> 00:38:01,780
(Ke Stubborn is the mastermind
who framed the Longdong Army)

1163
00:38:01,820 --> 00:38:02,620
(Yang Glory's motives:)

1164
00:38:02,620 --> 00:38:03,780
(Against Ke Stubborn: Suspected
forgery and sought revenge)

1165
00:38:03,780 --> 00:38:04,820
(Against Chancellor Tui: None)

1166
00:38:04,820 --> 00:38:06,480
