1203
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:14,480
Chancellor Tui.

1204
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:15,580
(Disguise Card: 3-minute limit)

1205
00:39:16,060 --> 00:39:19,220
(Disguise Card: 3-minute limit)

1206
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:20,200
