1250
00:40:50,960 --> 00:40:51,640
No.

1251
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:52,680
Is being cocky illegal?

1252
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:53,240
No.

1253
00:40:53,480 --> 00:40:55,240
If being cocky were illegal, we'd...

1254
