1292
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:00,160
Zuixian Inn.

1293
00:42:00,160 --> 00:42:00,760
Got it.

1294
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:01,400
Okay.

1295
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:03,480
