1349
00:43:45,240 --> 00:43:47,440
A member of Kuang's royal family.

1350
00:43:47,440 --> 00:43:48,080
Life-Guarding Bell.

1351
00:43:48,080 --> 00:43:49,200
Ring the Life-Guarding Bell.

1352
00:43:49,200 --> 00:43:51,160
Shadow Guard Ke Wu.

1353
00:43:51,160 --> 00:43:52,560
Prince Wu.

1354
00:43:52,560 --> 00:43:54,960
Hear the bell, start fighting.

1355
