1358
00:44:05,720 --> 00:44:06,320
No.

1359
00:44:06,380 --> 00:44:07,380
(Why does Jin's bell make Ke dance?)
How did you...

1360
00:44:08,200 --> 00:44:09,640
She's royalty too?

1361
