2195
01:11:04,640 --> 01:11:06,640
(The wound medicine belongs to Ke)
When I opened it

2196
01:11:06,640 --> 01:11:07,480
and smelled it,

2197
01:11:07,480 --> 01:11:08,840
I realized

2198
01:11:09,360 --> 01:11:11,400
the assassin from back then

2199
01:11:11,400 --> 01:11:13,360
smelled exactly like

2200
01:11:13,920 --> 01:11:14,640
this medicine.

2201
01:11:14,640 --> 01:11:16,480
And it's a secret formula.

2202
01:11:16,780 --> 01:11:18,620
(Ke Stubborn was the assassin)

2203
01:11:18,640 --> 01:11:21,440
And I know this sword well.

2204
01:11:21,440 --> 01:11:24,000
It's the one he always carries,

2205
01:11:24,000 --> 01:11:25,600
the Moonlight Toothpick Sword.

2206
01:11:26,510 --> 01:11:28,150
(Concerned citizen)
Why are you killing people everywhere?

2207
01:11:28,720 --> 01:11:30,320
So the one who tried to kill me

2208
01:11:30,320 --> 01:11:32,800
and ultimately caused the war

2209
01:11:33,540 --> 01:11:34,200
(Big bad guy)

2210
01:11:34,200 --> 01:11:35,160
was none other

2211
01:11:35,760 --> 01:11:36,400
than him.

2212
01:11:37,800 --> 01:11:40,640
You've also been secretly
helping my brother.

2213
01:11:40,880 --> 01:11:41,840
I haven't helped anyone.

2214
01:11:41,840 --> 01:11:43,280
I've only ever helped her.

2215
01:11:47,400 --> 01:11:47,880
So in the end,

2216
01:11:47,880 --> 01:11:49,200
Kuang was behind all this.

2217
01:11:49,200 --> 01:11:49,800
One spread lies,

2218
01:11:49,800 --> 01:11:50,740
(Spreading lies)
and the other was...

2219
01:11:50,740 --> 01:11:51,860
(Stirring up trouble)

2220
01:11:53,520 --> 01:11:54,320
So,

2221
01:11:54,600 --> 01:11:55,920
someone like him,

2222
01:11:55,920 --> 01:11:56,560
a menace,

2223
01:11:56,560 --> 01:11:57,560
had to die.

2224
01:11:57,580 --> 01:11:58,340
(Ding Pillar's motive, against
Ke Stubborn: Ke tried to kill him,)

2225
01:11:58,340 --> 01:11:59,180
(And he learned Ke was secretly helping
his brother, so he wanted revenge)

2226
01:11:59,180 --> 01:11:59,900
(Against Chancellor Tui: None)

2227
01:11:59,920 --> 01:12:00,560
Okay.

2228
01:12:00,560 --> 01:12:04,600
So, were you the one who ambushed him

2229
01:12:04,600 --> 01:12:05,800
and tried to kill him?

2230
01:12:06,640 --> 01:12:07,800
After hearing his story,

2231
01:12:07,800 --> 01:12:08,520
I realized something.

2232
01:12:09,440 --> 01:12:11,480
You're seriously hard to kill.

2233
01:12:12,000 --> 01:12:14,880
I tried to kill you twice.

2234
01:12:14,880 --> 01:12:15,800
Both times,

2235
01:12:15,800 --> 01:12:17,600
Chancellor Kuang ordered me to.

2236
01:12:17,600 --> 01:12:18,240
Chancellor Kuang?

2237
01:12:18,240 --> 01:12:19,380
(Kuang ordered the assassination)
That's right.

2238
01:12:19,400 --> 01:12:21,560
I've rarely missed my whole life.

2239
01:12:21,560 --> 01:12:22,600
But the first time

2240
01:12:22,600 --> 01:12:23,600
I tried to kill him,

2241
01:12:23,600 --> 01:12:25,960
he had too many guards around him.

2242
01:12:25,960 --> 01:12:27,680
So I couldn't do it.

2243
01:12:27,680 --> 01:12:28,760
Instead, I picked up

2244
01:12:28,760 --> 01:12:29,920
the seal he'd dropped

2245
01:12:29,920 --> 01:12:30,840
and brought it

2246
01:12:31,320 --> 01:12:32,080
to Chancellor Kuang.

2247
01:12:32,730 --> 01:12:34,040
(The seal once fell into Kuang's hands)
But he wasn't satisfied.

2248
01:12:34,040 --> 01:12:35,360
He still wanted him dead.

2249
01:12:35,360 --> 01:12:36,640
So he sent me after him again.

2250
01:12:36,640 --> 01:12:37,600
That was my second attempt.

2251
01:12:37,840 --> 01:12:38,680
The second time,

2252
01:12:38,680 --> 01:12:40,120
I tracked him to Old Fall Cliff.

2253
01:12:40,760 --> 01:12:42,520
This time, he didn't have many guards.

2254
01:12:42,520 --> 01:12:43,280
He was alone.

2255
01:12:43,440 --> 01:12:44,520
I jumped off my horse

2256
01:12:44,520 --> 01:12:46,520
(Ke Stubborn, Ding Pillar)
and slashed his left shoulder.

2257
01:12:46,920 --> 01:12:48,160
Then I fell off the cliff too.

2258
01:12:48,880 --> 01:12:50,440
In Year 255 of Tui,

2259
01:12:50,440 --> 01:12:52,920
I fell from the cliff

2260
01:12:53,400 --> 01:12:56,160
and landed on a man's back.

2261
01:12:56,560 --> 01:12:57,640
It was him.

2262
01:12:57,640 --> 01:12:59,380
(Ke Stubborn was rescued by Ning in 255
and became Shi Damen's junior disciple)

2263
01:12:59,880 --> 01:13:00,600
You failed again.

2264
01:13:01,280 --> 01:13:03,120
(This assassin's kind of bad)
He fell off a cliff.

2265
01:13:03,120 --> 01:13:04,080
How was I supposed to know

2266
01:13:04,520 --> 01:13:05,560
(Minor injuries)
he'd be rescued

2267
01:13:05,560 --> 01:13:06,680
and nursed for three years?

2268
01:13:06,680 --> 01:13:08,160
In that case,

2269
01:13:08,160 --> 01:13:10,160
since you're so hard to kill,

2270
01:13:10,160 --> 01:13:11,580
I'll just try again.

2271
01:13:11,580 --> 01:13:12,280
(Redeem myself)

2272
01:13:12,280 --> 01:13:13,440
Don't kill him!

2273
01:13:13,440 --> 01:13:14,880
Keep him alive and torture him.

2274
01:13:14,880 --> 01:13:15,920
Make him marry me!

2275
01:13:16,180 --> 01:13:17,860
(#Sentenced to life by love)

2276
01:13:17,880 --> 01:13:19,340
Make his life miserable!

2277
01:13:20,600 --> 01:13:21,920
(Have some dignity)
Your Highness, no.

2278
01:13:21,920 --> 01:13:24,400
No. Do you know why I rejected you?

2279
01:13:24,840 --> 01:13:27,240
We made another agreement back then.

2280
01:13:27,240 --> 01:13:29,040
(The crown prince had his reasons)
Yes. Ever since we

2281
01:13:29,040 --> 01:13:30,480
met at the peace conference,

2282
01:13:30,480 --> 01:13:31,600
we've agreed

2283
01:13:31,600 --> 01:13:33,000
on one thing.

2284
01:13:33,520 --> 01:13:35,120
For peace across the realm,

2285
01:13:35,120 --> 01:13:36,440
we won't marry.

2286
01:13:36,880 --> 01:13:38,880
We have to preserve this peace.

2287
01:13:39,520 --> 01:13:40,840
We won't form a marriage alliance.

2288
01:13:41,600 --> 01:13:42,760
Expanding our territory

2289
01:13:42,760 --> 01:13:45,320
(Bound by this pact, in life and death)
would only displace people.

2290
01:13:45,520 --> 01:13:46,440
(End war. Protect the people)
What we want

2291
01:13:46,440 --> 01:13:48,600
(No home before peace)
is to hear the people's

2292
01:13:48,600 --> 01:13:50,720
(The princes' shared vow)
true wishes.

2293
01:13:50,740 --> 01:13:53,260
(Two crown princes who stand for peace)

2294
01:13:55,400 --> 01:13:56,360
I get it.

2295
01:13:56,600 --> 01:13:57,960
They'd already made a deal.

2296
01:13:57,960 --> 01:14:00,240
Whoever married the Princess of Kuang

2297
01:14:00,240 --> 01:14:01,560
would become more powerful.

2298
01:14:01,560 --> 01:14:02,240
Right. It'd upset the balance.

2299
01:14:02,240 --> 01:14:03,600
(A marriage would upset the balance)
So they wanted to preserve

2300
01:14:03,600 --> 01:14:06,320
the balance among all three kingdoms.

2301
01:14:06,320 --> 01:14:07,200
That shows both crown princes

2302
01:14:07,200 --> 01:14:08,520
would make wise rulers.

2303
01:14:08,520 --> 01:14:09,560
Of course.

2304
01:14:09,560 --> 01:14:10,440
My friend.

2305
01:14:10,800 --> 01:14:12,520
But there's someone

2306
01:14:12,520 --> 01:14:15,080
who I think has been stirring up trouble

2307
01:14:15,080 --> 01:14:16,040
among our three kingdoms.

2308
01:14:16,040 --> 01:14:17,760
It's Chancellor Tui, right?

2309
01:14:17,760 --> 01:14:20,600
(Tui is the real cause of the conflict)
He had Kuang's guard

2310
01:14:20,600 --> 01:14:22,760
keep trying to kill Li's crown prince.

2311
01:14:22,760 --> 01:14:23,120
Yes.

2312
01:14:23,320 --> 01:14:24,970
(Tui ordered the hit on Prince of Li)
Chancellor Kuang

2313
01:14:25,000 --> 01:14:26,200
(Tui is actually Kuang)
became Chancellor Tui.

2314
01:14:26,200 --> 01:14:27,320
They're actually the same person.

2315
01:14:28,760 --> 01:14:29,920
Most likely,

2316
01:14:29,920 --> 01:14:30,600
I think.

2317
01:14:30,600 --> 01:14:32,440
But now there's another problem.

2318
01:14:33,120 --> 01:14:35,560
None of us currently has a motive

2319
01:14:35,560 --> 01:14:36,760
to kill Chancellor Kuang,

2320
01:14:36,760 --> 01:14:38,320
who may also be Chancellor Tui.

2321
01:14:38,320 --> 01:14:39,120
No motive at all.

2322
01:14:39,880 --> 01:14:40,240
Right.

2323
01:14:40,240 --> 01:14:41,200
(No one has an obvious motive
to kill Chancellor Tui)

2324
01:14:41,200 --> 01:14:42,560
There's no clear motive.

2325
01:14:42,560 --> 01:14:43,280
That's right.

2326
01:14:43,280 --> 01:14:44,680
My motive

2327
01:14:45,120 --> 01:14:46,040
was to kill her.

2328
01:14:46,620 --> 01:14:47,420
(Ning Bowei's motive)
Because I believed

2329
01:14:47,420 --> 01:14:48,440
(Against Yang: Suspected she was a spy)
she was from Li.

2330
01:14:48,440 --> 01:14:50,540
(Against Chancellor Tui: None)
She wrote that letter.

2331
01:14:50,560 --> 01:14:51,440
So you wanted to kill me?

2332
01:14:51,440 --> 01:14:53,080
(Targets: Ning, Yang)
Yes. She was my target.

2333
01:14:53,080 --> 01:14:54,840
But who were you trying to kill?

2334
01:14:54,840 --> 01:14:55,920
You wanted to kill him.

2335
01:14:56,420 --> 01:14:57,120
(Yang Glory's motive)
Yes.

2336
01:14:57,120 --> 01:14:58,160
Against Ke: Suspected forgery)
It's all connected.

2337
01:14:58,160 --> 01:14:58,820
(Wanted revenge for Longdong)
Right.

2338
01:14:58,840 --> 01:15:00,040
(Against Chancellor Tui: None)
I wanted to kill him.

2339
01:15:00,040 --> 01:15:00,800
You wanted to kill the crown prince.

2340
01:15:00,800 --> 01:15:02,520
(Targets: Yang, Ke. Ke's motive)
Because he's part of Tui's royal family.

2341
01:15:02,520 --> 01:15:03,420
(Against He Ha: Suspected Tui royalty)
That's right.

2342
01:15:03,440 --> 01:15:03,920
(To restore Kuang)
What about you?

2343
01:15:03,920 --> 01:15:05,800
(Against Chancellor Tui: None)
I wanted to kill Li's crown prince.

2344
01:15:05,800 --> 01:15:06,320
That's right.

2345
01:15:06,320 --> 01:15:06,960
(Targets: Ke, He)
Yes.

2346
01:15:06,960 --> 01:15:08,240
(He Ha's motive)
You wanted to kill Li's crown prince.

2347
01:15:08,240 --> 01:15:08,760
(Against Ding: Suspected he
was Li's crown prince)

2348
01:15:08,760 --> 01:15:10,760
(Against Tui: None)
And Li's prince wanted to kill him.

2349
01:15:10,780 --> 01:15:11,300
(Targets: He, Ding)

2350
01:15:11,300 --> 01:15:11,960
(Ding Pillar's motive)

2351
01:15:11,960 --> 01:15:13,560
(Against Ke: Suspected assassin)
Did we just form a five-pointed star?

2352
01:15:13,560 --> 01:15:14,540
(Against Tui: None. Targets: Ding, Ke)
Yes.

2353
01:15:14,700 --> 01:15:15,330
(Murder motives)

2354
01:15:15,330 --> 01:15:16,240
(Prince of Tui: Suspected Ding was Li's
true crown prince and wanted revenge)

2355
01:15:16,240 --> 01:15:17,150
(Li's true crown prince: Suspected Ke
was the assassin and wanted revenge)

2356
01:15:17,150 --> 01:15:18,290
(Kuang guard: Suspected He was
Tui royalty and wanted to restore Kuang)

2357
01:15:18,290 --> 01:15:19,060
(Eagle founder: Suspected Ke forged
the letter and wanted revenge)

2358
01:15:19,070 --> 01:15:19,860
(Longdong commander: Suspected Yang
was a Li spy and wanted revenge)

2359
01:15:19,860 --> 01:15:20,560
(Zuixian Inn)

2360
01:15:20,560 --> 01:15:22,560
Alright. Let's get out of here.

2361
01:15:22,560 --> 01:15:22,920
Let's go.

2362
01:15:24,400 --> 01:15:25,320
What's this?

2363
01:15:26,400 --> 01:15:27,360
What's this?

2364
01:15:27,360 --> 01:15:27,680
What?

2365
01:15:28,420 --> 01:15:29,540
(Chancellor Tui's secret plot)

2366
01:15:29,560 --> 01:15:30,280
Here's what happened.

2367
01:15:31,000 --> 01:15:32,240
On the 27th,

2368
01:15:32,240 --> 01:15:34,240
I went back to my room
and noticed something.

2369
01:15:35,240 --> 01:15:36,680
The Qide Sword

2370
01:15:36,780 --> 01:15:38,060
(May 27, to keep the Qide Sword safe)
had originally been with me.

2371
01:15:38,060 --> 01:15:38,460
(Ning removed the Qide Sword from
Shi Damen's tomb and kept it himself)

2372
01:15:38,880 --> 01:15:40,000
But when I returned,

2373
01:15:40,000 --> 01:15:41,520
the Qide Sword was gone.

2374
01:15:41,620 --> 01:15:42,480
(The Qide Sword
mysteriously disappeared?)

2375
01:15:42,480 --> 01:15:43,720
I suspected

2376
01:15:44,200 --> 01:15:46,240
Chivalry Manor might be involved.

2377
01:15:46,680 --> 01:15:48,440
So I decided to go there

2378
01:15:48,440 --> 01:15:50,440
and look for the Qide Sword.

2379
01:15:50,680 --> 01:15:51,840
But when I tried to investigate,

2380
01:15:51,840 --> 01:15:53,680
I found Chancellor Tui

2381
01:15:53,680 --> 01:15:55,600
plotting something with someone.

2382
01:15:56,160 --> 01:15:57,040
(Ning Waver discovered this on the 27th)
I wanted to sneak in and listen.

2383
01:15:57,040 --> 01:15:59,120
(Chancellor plotting at Chivalry Manor)
But the Netherworld Elders were there.

2384
01:15:59,120 --> 01:16:00,840
They're insanely good fighters.

2385
01:16:00,840 --> 01:16:01,720
So I

2386
01:16:01,720 --> 01:16:02,640
got a little scared.

2387
01:16:03,120 --> 01:16:03,880
I couldn't beat them.

2388
01:16:03,880 --> 01:16:06,320
So I quietly slipped away and went back.

2389
01:16:07,080 --> 01:16:08,480
Let's go check it out now.

2390
01:16:09,120 --> 01:16:09,400
Okay.

2391
01:16:10,200 --> 01:16:13,160
(Chivalry Manor)
Let's head to Chivalry Manor now.

2392
01:16:13,680 --> 01:16:14,680
We'll get to the bottom of this.

2393
01:16:16,560 --> 01:16:17,560
Okay.

2394
01:16:17,560 --> 01:16:18,600
We're at the meeting hall.

2395
01:16:20,900 --> 01:16:23,420
(Mourning)

2396
01:16:31,260 --> 01:16:33,220
(Mourning)

2397
01:16:35,640 --> 01:16:36,560
Anything different?

2398
01:16:40,000 --> 01:16:41,400
They switched to longer burial mats.

2399
01:16:41,900 --> 01:16:43,220
(Five days ago)

2400
01:16:43,540 --> 01:16:44,900
(Super memory)

2401
01:16:45,160 --> 01:16:46,400
Body collection records.

2402
01:16:46,400 --> 01:16:48,060
(Body collection records)

2403
01:16:48,240 --> 01:16:49,160
Wait.

2404
01:16:50,200 --> 01:16:51,880
Four bodies collected today.

2405
01:16:51,880 --> 01:16:53,200
He Ha.

2406
01:16:55,640 --> 01:16:57,200
Ding Pillar.

2407
01:16:57,200 --> 01:16:59,040
Yang Glory.

2408
01:16:59,040 --> 01:17:00,720
Ke Stubborn.

2409
01:17:01,200 --> 01:17:03,680
All had no family or friends, or

2410
01:17:03,680 --> 01:17:05,560
their relatives were missing.

2411
01:17:05,560 --> 01:17:06,920
Wrapped in a straw mat

2412
01:17:06,920 --> 01:17:08,720
and buried in the courtyard.

2413
01:17:09,640 --> 01:17:10,340
(He Ha, Ke Stubborn,)
Wait.

2414
01:17:10,340 --> 01:17:10,960
(Ding Pillar, Yang Glory)
Wait.

2415
01:17:10,960 --> 01:17:12,580
(All four are dead)
How could I be dead?

2416
01:17:12,600 --> 01:17:13,960
I'm dead?

2417
01:17:15,920 --> 01:17:16,680
No.

2418
01:17:16,680 --> 01:17:17,720
Ning Waver isn't here.

2419
01:17:17,720 --> 01:17:19,240
Ning Waver was already dead.

2420
01:17:19,240 --> 01:17:21,680
(Ning died on the 27th)
No need to collect Ning's body.

2421
01:17:21,680 --> 01:17:23,680
Ning Waver

2422
01:17:23,680 --> 01:17:24,120
is

2423
01:17:24,120 --> 01:17:24,760
You said I died?

2424
01:17:24,760 --> 01:17:25,680
is already dead.

2425
01:17:26,680 --> 01:17:28,480
When I came back again,

2426
01:17:28,480 --> 01:17:30,000
I saw that Ning Waver
had come back to life.

2427
01:17:30,760 --> 01:17:33,340
(Everyone revived like Ning)
He died on the 27th.

2428
01:17:33,400 --> 01:17:35,600
I'm the only one alive.
Don't mess with me.

2429
01:17:42,160 --> 01:17:44,960
Let me out!

2430
01:17:45,480 --> 01:17:47,280
And then the door
actually opened for you.

2431
01:17:47,300 --> 01:17:49,380
(Now that it's open,
you're too scared to go)

2432
01:17:49,840 --> 01:17:50,480
Wait.

2433
01:17:50,480 --> 01:17:52,520
Let's open this straw mat
and take a look. Come on.

2434
01:17:53,080 --> 01:17:53,600
This...

2435
01:17:54,720 --> 01:17:55,320
No need to open it.

2436
01:17:55,320 --> 01:17:56,120
It's empty.

2437
01:17:56,120 --> 01:17:56,640
Empty.

2438
01:17:56,700 --> 01:17:58,300
(These straw mats once
held everyone's bodies)

2439
01:17:58,600 --> 01:17:59,960
Wait. What's this brick doing here?

2440
01:18:00,440 --> 01:18:01,080
A headrest.

2441
01:18:01,080 --> 01:18:02,000
(A brick beside the straw mat)
No.

2442
01:18:02,000 --> 01:18:03,000
No.

2443
01:18:03,000 --> 01:18:03,880
There's blood on it.

2444
01:18:04,300 --> 01:18:05,480
(Bloodstains on the brick)

2445
01:18:05,480 --> 01:18:06,920
A crucial piece of evidence.

2446
01:18:07,600 --> 01:18:08,720
What's this? It's a needle.

2447
01:18:09,380 --> 01:18:11,540
(A needle and iron ball by another mat)
Is that the Corn Blossom Needle?

2448
01:18:11,580 --> 01:18:12,800
(It's Yang's signature move,
the Corn Blossom Needle?)

2449
01:18:12,800 --> 01:18:13,920
This is what you used to kill

2450
01:18:13,920 --> 01:18:15,480
Ke Stubborn,

2451
01:18:15,480 --> 01:18:15,960
right?

2452
01:18:15,980 --> 01:18:17,740
(Yang Glory attacked
and killed Ke Stubborn)

2453
01:18:18,080 --> 01:18:18,440
Yes.

2454
01:18:19,080 --> 01:18:20,040
But I only had this marble.

2455
