The moment they come in,

2719
01:26:25,360 --> 01:26:27,000
someone behind them shuts the door.

2720
01:26:27,000 --> 01:26:28,120
And locks themselves inside?

2721
01:26:28,140 --> 01:26:30,000
(You've been locked up too long)

2722
01:26:30,000 --> 01:26:30,400
No.

2723
01:26:30,400 --> 01:26:32,280
Lock them inside.

2724
01:26:32,280 --> 01:26:33,360
Why would we lock ourselves in?

2725
01:26:33,360 --> 01:26:34,160
We need the key.

2726
01:26:34,640 --> 01:26:35,560
So in the end,

2727
01:26:35,560 --> 01:26:37,360
we lure all of them into this cage

2728
01:26:37,360 --> 01:26:37,920
and lock them together.

2729
01:26:37,920 --> 01:26:39,080
Then we go in and get the key.

2730
01:26:39,080 --> 01:26:39,520
Then we leave.

2731
01:26:39,520 --> 01:26:40,200
Right.

2732
01:26:40,200 --> 01:26:43,020
(Trap the ghost soldiers,
then get the key)

2733
01:26:43,040 --> 01:26:44,840
Maybe this cage can move.

2734
01:26:45,920 --> 01:26:46,320
Yeah.

2735
01:26:46,320 --> 01:26:46,920
(Breaking in five days ago)

2736
01:26:46,920 --> 01:26:47,960
(Experience comes in handy today)
We definitely have to push it.

2737
01:26:47,960 --> 01:26:49,200
(The small cage can move)
Maybe we lift it first,

2738
01:26:49,200 --> 01:26:50,640
then move it.

2739
01:26:50,640 --> 01:26:51,560
Move it...

2740
01:26:51,560 --> 01:26:52,800
So the doors line up?

2741
01:26:53,220 --> 01:26:56,020
(Where is the big cage's door?)

2742
01:26:56,360 --> 01:26:57,600
Let me think about the layout.

2743
01:26:57,600 --> 01:26:58,520
How many doors are there?

2744
01:26:59,400 --> 01:27:00,520
Three doors total.

2745
01:27:01,900 --> 01:27:03,100
(Night vision mode)

2746
01:27:03,120 --> 01:27:04,760
(Five days ago in the cell)
Kill me.

2747
01:27:05,200 --> 01:27:06,840
It's fine. I'm not scared at all.

2748
01:27:07,820 --> 01:27:09,180
(Quietly studies the cage's layout)

2749
01:27:09,200 --> 01:27:09,880
I see it.

2750
01:27:11,280 --> 01:27:12,720
This door.

2751
01:27:12,720 --> 01:27:13,920
(Door 1, Door 2)

2752
01:27:13,920 --> 01:27:15,040
(Door 3)
And this door.

2753
01:27:15,040 --> 01:27:16,200
One, two, three doors.

2754
01:27:16,200 --> 01:27:17,640
Three doors total.

2755
01:27:17,660 --> 01:27:20,260
(The god of details)

2756
01:27:20,520 --> 01:27:21,480
Then it's easy.

2757
01:27:21,960 --> 01:27:24,000
Just line this door up with their exit.

2758
01:27:24,000 --> 01:27:25,320
Then send them straight in.

2759
01:27:25,320 --> 01:27:26,160
That makes sense.

2760
01:27:26,580 --> 01:27:27,440
(Connect the big and small cages)
Come on.

2761
01:27:27,440 --> 01:27:28,540
(Lure soldiers into the small cage)
Let's go.

2762
01:27:28,560 --> 01:27:29,000
Come on.

2763
01:27:29,000 --> 01:27:29,600
Watch your hands.

2764
01:27:35,600 --> 01:27:37,200
Let's leave this door for now.

2765
01:27:37,200 --> 01:27:38,240
I'll open this one first.

2766
01:27:38,240 --> 01:27:38,720
Okay.

2767
01:27:38,880 --> 01:27:40,440
(Everyone else is in the safe zone)
Then open this door.

2768
01:27:40,440 --> 01:27:41,880
(Exit)
Then these connect, right?

2769
01:27:41,880 --> 01:27:42,200
Right.

2770
01:27:42,200 --> 01:27:43,360
Once these are connected,

2771
01:27:43,360 --> 01:27:44,600
they can actually come over here.

2772
01:27:45,760 --> 01:27:46,680
You get what I mean?

2773
01:27:46,680 --> 01:27:48,360
These two doors also form a wall.

2774
01:27:48,360 --> 01:27:49,840
Got it.

2775
01:27:49,840 --> 01:27:52,160
But why would they come in here?

2776
01:27:52,180 --> 01:27:54,460
(Will the ghost soldiers
really enter the small cage?)

2777
01:27:54,480 --> 01:27:57,280
These ghost soldiers
seem drawn to living people.

2778
01:27:57,300 --> 01:28:00,380
(They gather on the side with people)

2779
01:28:00,520 --> 01:28:01,520
We need someone to lure them.

2780
01:28:01,520 --> 01:28:03,400
(Use a living person as bait)
This is only step one. Look.

2781
01:28:03,400 --> 01:28:05,960
Come on. Let's set it up like he said.

2782
01:28:05,960 --> 01:28:07,080
See? This blocks it off.

2783
01:28:07,080 --> 01:28:08,160
Okay. Then what?

2784
01:28:08,160 --> 01:28:09,480
Then when we open this door,

2785
01:28:09,480 --> 01:28:10,520
it swings this way.

2786
01:28:10,520 --> 01:28:11,760
So it becomes another wall.

2787
01:28:11,760 --> 01:28:13,360
Then we need someone inside.

2788
01:28:14,040 --> 01:28:15,640
Then open this door.

2789
01:28:17,560 --> 01:28:19,160
(Everyone else is in the safe zone)
Then the moment you open that door,

2790
01:28:19,160 --> 01:28:20,160
they'll charge at me.

2791
01:28:20,160 --> 01:28:22,480
Once they charge at me, I'll do this.

2792
01:28:22,480 --> 01:28:23,280
Then they'll be blocked in.

2793
01:28:23,280 --> 01:28:25,320
Right. Let's try it first.

2794
01:28:28,940 --> 01:28:31,860
(The two cages
are successfully connected)

2795
01:28:36,380 --> 01:28:39,220
(They only move toward people)

2796
01:28:40,280 --> 01:28:42,320
We need someone standing up front.

2797
01:28:42,320 --> 01:28:43,920
All of us living people
need to stand over there.

2798
01:28:43,940 --> 01:28:49,100
(Leave it to the Jinyi Guards)

2799
01:28:51,000 --> 01:28:51,760
There's one over there.

2800
01:28:51,760 --> 01:28:53,240
Okay. We need to get the key over there.

2801
01:28:54,060 --> 01:28:56,380
(No ghost soldiers
are guarding beneath the key)

2802
01:28:58,780 --> 01:29:01,140
(Giving it everything they've got)

2803
01:29:01,560 --> 01:29:02,680
He, hold this door.

2804
01:29:02,680 --> 01:29:03,800
I'll get the key.

2805
01:29:05,100 --> 01:29:07,740
(I'm coming to help you, Your Highness)

2806
01:29:11,680 --> 01:29:12,520
I can't get it down.

2807
01:29:13,040 --> 01:29:13,880
Does anyone have scissors?

2808
01:29:14,720 --> 01:29:15,480
I can't untie it.

2809
01:29:16,480 --> 01:29:18,120
Jin, can you do it?

2810
01:29:19,560 --> 01:29:20,440
Don't go over there!

2811
01:29:21,920 --> 01:29:23,180
Come and get me.

2812
01:29:23,180 --> 01:29:24,360
(Drawing their attention)

2813
01:29:24,360 --> 01:29:25,520
Come get me!

2814
01:29:25,640 --> 01:29:26,760
Don't go over there!

2815
01:29:29,780 --> 01:29:31,980
(The ghost soldiers are drawn
to people. Failed to get the key)

2816
01:29:32,000 --> 01:29:33,160
So it's not that easy, huh?

2817
01:29:33,360 --> 01:29:35,080
No, it's tied with

2818
01:29:35,080 --> 01:29:36,280
a hemp rope.

2819
01:29:36,720 --> 01:29:37,600
It's tied tight.

2820
01:29:38,160 --> 01:29:40,300
(Can't get the key from outside)
We have to go in.

2821
01:29:40,320 --> 01:29:41,880
So there's no solution right now, right?

2822
01:29:41,880 --> 01:29:42,960
Let's lure them back.

2823
01:29:42,960 --> 01:29:44,240
Then we'll rethink this.

2824
01:29:44,800 --> 01:29:45,360
Okay.

2825
01:29:45,360 --> 01:29:45,800
Come on.

2826
01:29:47,900 --> 01:29:49,820
(Retreat!)

2827
01:29:51,080 --> 01:29:51,760
Close the door first.

2828
01:29:52,160 --> 01:29:54,440
Come on!

2829
01:29:56,980 --> 01:29:59,300
(Starting over)

2830
01:29:59,480 --> 01:30:01,080
This idea has to be right.

2831
01:30:01,080 --> 01:30:01,960
But how

2832
01:30:01,960 --> 01:30:03,400
do we lure them all over here

2833
01:30:03,400 --> 01:30:04,720
and lock them inside?

2834
01:30:05,480 --> 01:30:06,440
That's the key part.

2835
01:30:06,440 --> 01:30:08,860
(They can only get the key
after trapping the ghost soldiers)

2836
01:30:09,640 --> 01:30:10,760
There must be a way to position it,

2837
01:30:10,760 --> 01:30:11,760
that'll...

2838
01:30:12,280 --> 01:30:13,320
Keep them trapped outside.

2839
01:30:13,320 --> 01:30:15,560
Right. We need them focused
on just one person.

2840
01:30:15,560 --> 01:30:17,280
And we still need to be safe.

2841
01:30:17,880 --> 01:30:19,800
At the same time, what
do we need to make sure of?

2842
01:30:19,800 --> 01:30:20,720
We need to make sure

2843
01:30:20,720 --> 01:30:21,880
the space inside this cage

2844
01:30:21,880 --> 01:30:24,920
connects to the door we need to unlock.

2845
01:30:25,500 --> 01:30:32,220
(How can they avoid the ghost soldiers,
get the key, and escape?)

2846
01:30:32,720 --> 01:30:35,680
This takes really
good spatial awareness.

2847
01:30:35,680 --> 01:30:36,240
Spatial awareness.

2848
01:30:36,240 --> 01:30:37,600
Spatial reasoning.

2849
01:30:40,000 --> 01:30:41,720
I seriously want
to just go in and grab it.

2850
01:30:41,780 --> 01:30:43,020
(I'm losing my patience)

2851
01:30:43,360 --> 01:30:44,640
No, this...

2852
01:30:45,160 --> 01:30:46,280
What's this connected to?

2853
01:30:46,940 --> 01:30:50,300
(There's a chain on the wall)

2854
01:30:50,320 --> 01:30:51,000
This connects...

2855
01:30:51,000 --> 01:30:52,400
Look, that has a lock.

2856
01:30:52,920 --> 01:30:53,800
Could it connect to that?

2857
01:30:53,800 --> 01:30:55,620
(There's a ring on the cage door)

2858
01:30:59,600 --> 01:31:00,680
There must be a way to position it,

2859
01:31:00,680 --> 01:31:03,400
so they'll only focus on one person.

2860
01:31:03,400 --> 01:31:05,320
And we'll still be safe.

2861
01:31:05,800 --> 01:31:07,000
What's this connected to?

2862
01:31:07,000 --> 01:31:08,240
Look, that has a lock.

2863
01:31:08,840 --> 01:31:09,680
Could it connect to that?

2864
01:31:10,480 --> 01:31:11,920
This door.

2865
01:31:13,120 --> 01:31:14,280
And this door.

2866
01:31:14,280 --> 01:31:15,400
One, two, three doors.

2867
01:31:18,100 --> 01:31:19,060
(Reporting in)

2868
01:31:19,080 --> 01:31:20,200
This can close too.

2869
01:31:20,700 --> 01:31:21,640
(The forgotten door)

2870
01:31:21,640 --> 01:31:23,200
We open this door.

2871
01:31:23,200 --> 01:31:24,640
(Exit)
Then once we lure them over,

2872
01:31:24,640 --> 01:31:25,680
we just take this door,

2873
01:31:26,200 --> 01:31:28,000
block them off, and latch it.
Wouldn't that work?

2874
01:31:28,000 --> 01:31:29,480
Then close that side too.

2875
01:31:29,480 --> 01:31:31,080
Then they'll all be stuck over here.

2876
01:31:31,080 --> 01:31:32,080
Okay.

2877
01:31:32,080 --> 01:31:34,080
I don't think we even need this cage.

2878
01:31:34,080 --> 01:31:34,880
We don't.

2879
01:31:36,120 --> 01:31:37,200
Or we could just use this cage

2880
01:31:37,680 --> 01:31:39,280
as a wall.

2881
01:31:39,280 --> 01:31:39,880
Right here.

2882
01:31:40,320 --> 01:31:41,600
Use it as a wall right here.

2883
01:31:42,920 --> 01:31:44,440
(Overhead view of the cell, Exit)
Once this door opens,

2884
01:31:44,440 --> 01:31:45,920
we all walk this way.

2885
01:31:47,640 --> 01:31:48,000
Right.

2886
01:31:48,000 --> 01:31:49,160
Once we get over here,

2887
01:31:49,160 --> 01:31:51,160
we close this door

2888
01:31:51,160 --> 01:31:52,160
and latch it.

2889
01:31:52,160 --> 01:31:54,320
(Safe zone)
Then they'll be blocked off.

2890
01:31:54,600 --> 01:31:55,320
That works.

2891
01:31:55,320 --> 01:31:56,280
Yeah. That's it.

2892
01:31:56,280 --> 01:31:57,480
That'll definitely work.

2893
01:31:57,480 --> 01:31:59,040
Let's try it.

2894
01:31:59,040 --> 01:31:59,560
Okay.

2895
01:31:59,880 --> 01:32:01,600
How do we secure this?

2896
01:32:03,200 --> 01:32:03,760
Come closer.

2897
01:32:03,760 --> 01:32:06,420
(Securing the small cage
to block the path)

2898
01:32:06,460 --> 01:32:09,900
(One end is tied to the big cage)

2899
01:32:10,060 --> 01:32:11,720
(The other end is tied to the wall)
Done?

2900
01:32:11,720 --> 01:32:12,040
Yep.

2901
01:32:12,050 --> 01:32:13,000
Okay. The cage can't move now.

2902
01:32:13,200 --> 01:32:14,640
Come on. Let's lure
them from here together.

2903
01:32:15,080 --> 01:32:15,360
Okay.

2904
01:32:15,760 --> 01:32:17,560
Come on. Move back.

2905
01:32:17,560 --> 01:32:19,040
We'll get in front
and get ready. Go ahead.

2906
01:32:19,780 --> 01:32:22,020
(Ready for action)

2907
01:32:22,360 --> 01:32:25,240
(Bringing up the rear)
Go!

2908
01:32:28,000 --> 01:32:28,920
Get that ready first.

2909
01:32:28,920 --> 01:32:30,360
Open it.

2910
01:32:33,680 --> 01:32:34,800
Get in, quick!

2911
01:32:37,360 --> 01:32:38,960
Get in, quick!

2912
01:32:38,960 --> 01:32:39,760
Close the door!

2913
01:32:39,760 --> 01:32:40,480
Just close it!

2914
01:32:40,760 --> 01:32:42,640
Just lock it with the chain.

2915
01:32:42,740 --> 01:32:44,000
(Successfully traps ghost soldiers
outside the cage)

2916
01:32:44,000 --> 01:32:45,160
That was awesome!

2917
01:32:45,560 --> 01:32:46,200
That was awesome!

2918
01:32:47,060 --> 01:32:48,200
(I'm amazing)

2919
01:32:48,200 --> 01:32:49,080
Get the key.

2920
01:32:50,360 --> 01:32:51,960
It's tied really tight.

2921
01:32:51,960 --> 01:32:52,760
Yeah.

2922
01:32:52,760 --> 01:32:54,200
Otherwise we'd have gotten it earlier.

2923
01:32:55,900 --> 01:32:57,420
(Successfully gets the key)

2924
01:32:57,440 --> 01:32:58,120
Let's go, Ning.

2925
01:32:58,560 --> 01:32:59,280
Let's unlock the door.

2926
01:33:01,020 --> 01:33:03,060
(Successfully unlocks the door)

2927
01:33:05,600 --> 01:33:06,480
It's so hot.

2928
01:33:06,920 --> 01:33:08,720
Ghost soldiers, get some sun.

2929
01:33:08,720 --> 01:33:09,360
Get some vitamin D.

2930
01:33:10,140 --> 01:33:12,420
(Forget vitamin D. They need sunscreen)

2931
01:33:13,600 --> 01:33:14,880
Where are we now?

2932
01:33:14,880 --> 01:33:15,960
What's happening outside?

2933
01:33:16,400 --> 01:33:17,240
Smoke?

2934
01:33:17,240 --> 01:33:17,840
Look outside.

2935
01:33:20,400 --> 01:33:23,560
Yan Reason and Junzi Ruyu?

2936
01:33:23,560 --> 01:33:24,840
Senior, help!

2937
01:33:27,680 --> 01:33:29,200
Why are there more ghost soldiers?

2938
01:33:29,200 --> 01:33:31,120
Open the door!

2939
01:33:31,120 --> 01:33:31,800
Run!

2940
01:33:34,880 --> 01:33:35,560
Hurry!

2941
01:33:39,160 --> 01:33:39,760
Ning!

2942
01:33:39,820 --> 01:33:42,500
(Can they escape the ghost soldiers?)

2943
01:33:42,500 --> 01:33:51,900
(Mortuary)

2944
01:33:51,900 --> 01:33:53,280
(Hidden blades, hidden agendas)

2945
01:33:53,280 --> 01:33:53,940
(Qianji Pavilion)
We

2946
01:33:53,940 --> 01:33:55,480
(Next episode preview)
still need to go to Qianji Pavilion.

2947
01:33:55,480 --> 01:33:59,240
I'm sure someone here
has been here before.

2948
01:33:59,240 --> 01:34:00,320
What's his scheme?

2949
01:34:00,320 --> 01:34:01,560
Someone else is pulling the strings.

2950
01:34:01,560 --> 01:34:03,360
Does he want to unite the world...

2951
01:34:03,360 --> 01:34:05,920
Or tear it even further apart?

2952
01:34:05,920 --> 01:34:08,600
The Emperor has arrived!

2953
01:34:08,600 --> 01:34:11,520
Could it be that you're the power-hungry

2954
01:34:11,520 --> 01:34:12,720
Chancellor Kuang?

2955
01:34:12,720 --> 01:34:13,880
This is a trap.

2956
01:34:13,880 --> 01:34:15,240
(Schemes within schemes,
blind to the truth)

2957
01:34:15,240 --> 01:34:16,960
We still don't know how he killed him.

2958
01:34:16,960 --> 01:34:19,280
How did he die there?

2959
01:34:19,280 --> 01:34:20,480
Are we even alive or dead?

2960
01:34:20,480 --> 01:34:21,320
Whose imperial seal is it?

2961
01:34:21,320 --> 01:34:22,960
You've been here before?

2962
01:34:22,960 --> 01:34:24,200
I stayed hidden in the shadows.

2963
01:34:25,440 --> 01:34:26,480
He did this.

2964
01:34:26,480 --> 01:34:28,040
He's done nothing but evil.

2965
01:34:28,040 --> 01:34:29,080
He's way too smooth.

2966
01:34:29,080 --> 01:34:30,920
He uses pawns to frame people.

2967
01:34:30,920 --> 01:34:32,280
We're all his pawns.

2968
01:34:32,280 --> 01:34:33,300
(Step two: Weaken Tui Kingdom)
You have no evidence

2969
01:34:33,300 --> 01:34:34,520
that proves it was me.

2970
01:34:34,520 --> 01:34:35,640
I think there's been a misunderstanding.

2971
01:34:35,640 --> 01:34:36,840
He definitely had a motive to kill.

2972
01:34:36,840 --> 01:34:38,320
This person has
to meet three conditions.

2973
01:34:38,320 --> 01:34:39,520
Isn't he talking about you?

2974
01:34:39,520 --> 01:34:40,680
So you're the bad guy?

2975
01:34:40,680 --> 01:34:41,280
That's right.

2976
01:34:41,280 --> 01:34:42,280
Mystery solved!

2977
01:34:42,280 --> 01:34:43,520
Little killer.

2978
01:34:43,520 --> 01:34:44,240
Who's framing us?

2979
01:34:44,240 --> 01:34:45,040
Who's setting us up?

2980
01:34:45,040 --> 01:34:46,380
(Longdong in the wild,
defending the realm together)

2981
01:34:47,800 --> 01:34:48,280
Quick!

2982
01:34:48,280 --> 01:34:52,160
Everyone, a huge army
of ghost soldiers is coming!

2983
01:34:52,160 --> 01:34:53,720
Tui City is about to fall.

2984
01:34:53,720 --> 01:34:55,600
Only the Longdong Army can stop them.

2985
01:34:55,600 --> 01:34:57,000
Are we really going to war?

2986
01:34:57,000 --> 01:34:58,080
We're running out of time!

2987
01:34:58,080 --> 01:34:58,440
Quick!

2988
01:34:58,440 --> 01:35:00,440
The young commander
of the Longdong Army is here!

2989
01:35:00,440 --> 01:35:02,080
